  description="NodakMesh is North Dakota's community-driven mesh network. Using MeshCore and Meshtastic LoRa technology, we're building resilient, off-grid communication infrastructure across the Peace Garden State."
  keywords="NodakMesh, North Dakota mesh network, off-grid communication, LoRa mesh, MeshCore North Dakota, Meshtastic North Dakota, emergency communication ND, rural connectivity, mesh networking"
