          <span class="text-[--color-text-primary]">Connect Across</span>
          <br />
          <span class="gradient-text-animated">North Dakota</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-[--color-text-secondary] mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          NodakMesh is North Dakota's community-driven mesh network. Using MeshCore and Meshtastic,
          we're building resilient, off-grid communication infrastructure across the Peace Garden State.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/meshcore/getting-started" class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
            MeshCore Guide
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/meshtastic/getting-started" class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
            Meshtastic Guide
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scroll indicator -->
